        "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> Your last action was to deal piercing damage to an enemy within your reach</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> Attempt an Athletics check to [[/act grapple]] the same enemy. The weapon that dealt the triggering damage gains the grapple trait for this check. On a success, the target also takes @Damage[1d8[persistent,piercing]] damage (or @Damage[2d8[persistent,piercing]] damage on a critical success). When the target is no longer <u>Grabbed</u> or <u>Restrained</u> by you, the persistent damage ends.</p>",
